","context":"Люцифере","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077178\" id=\"note12b_p1\"><small>ГЕБР</small> ранкова зоря, син світанку. Правителя злочестивого світу (Вавилону) названо тут Люцифером, правителем усієї злочестивості. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/devil?lang=ukr\"><small>ПП</small> Диявол</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/lucifer?lang=ukr\">Люцифер</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/devil?lang=ukr","text":"ПП Диявол"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/lucifer?lang=ukr","text":"Люцифер"}]},"note13a":{"id":"note13a","marker":"13а","pid":"121077131","context":"Я","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077179\" id=\"note13a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.1-4?lang=ukr#p1\">Мойс. 4:1–4</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.1-4?lang=ukr#p1","text":"Мойс. 4:1–4"}]},"note13b":{"id":"note13b","marker":"13б","pid":"121077131","context":"півночі","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077180\" id=\"note13b_p1\"><small>ТОБТО</small> місце, де живуть боги, згідно з віруванням вавилонян. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/ps/48.3?lang=ukr#p3\">Пс. 48:3</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/ps/48.3?lang=ukr#p3","text":"Пс. 48:3"}]},"note15a":{"id":"note15a","marker":"15а","pid":"121077135","context":"прірви","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077181\" id=\"note15a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.3?lang=ukr#p3\">1 Неф. 14:3</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/14.3?lang=ukr#p3","text":"1 Неф. 14:3"}]},"note16a":{"id":"note16a","marker":"16а","pid":"121077137","context":"пильно","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077182\" id=\"note16a_p1\"><small>ГЕБР</small> дивляться скоса на тебе і розмірковують про тебе.</p>"},"note18a":{"id":"note18a","marker":"18а","pid":"121077141","context":"