Пр. 10:7</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/prov/10.7?lang=ukr#p7","text":"Пр. 10:7"}]},"note22b":{"id":"note22b","marker":"22б","pid":"121077149","context":"небожа","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077190\" id=\"note22b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/job/18.19?lang=ukr#p19\">Йов 18:19</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/job/18.19?lang=ukr#p19","text":"Йов 18:19"}]},"note23a":{"id":"note23a","marker":"23а","pid":"121077151","context":"володінням","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077191\" id=\"note23a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/34.11-15?lang=ukr#p11\">Ісая 34:11–15</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/34.11-15?lang=ukr#p11","text":"Ісая 34:11–15"}]},"note25a":{"id":"note25a","marker":"25а","pid":"121077155","context":"Асирійця","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077193\" id=\"note25a_p1\">Йдеться про напад Асирії та її поразку в Юдеї у 701 р. до <span class=\"small-caps\">р.х.</span> (<a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.24-27?lang=ukr#p24\">вірші 24–27</a>). <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/19.32-37?lang=ukr#p32\">2 Цар. 19:32–37</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/37.33-38?lang=ukr#p33\">Ісая 37:33–38</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/24.24-27?lang=ukr#p24","text":"вірші 24–27"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/19.32-37?lang=ukr#p32","text":"2 Цар. 19:32–37"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/37.33-38?lang=ukr#p33","text":"Ісая 37:33–38"}]},"note25b":{"id":"note25b","marker":"25б","pid":"121077155","context":"Моїх горах","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077195\" id=\"note25b_p1\"><small>ТОБТО</small> гори Юдеї та Ізраїля.</p>"},"note25c":{"id":"note25c","marker":"25в","pid":"121077155","context":"ярмо","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077196\" id=\"note25c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/10.27?lang=ukr#p27\">Ісая 10:27</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/isa/10.27?lang=ukr#p27","text":"Ісая 10:27"}]},"note26a":{"id":"note26a","marker":"26а","pid":"121077157","context":"Це","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077197\" id=\"note26a_p1\"><small>ТОБТО</small> з часом саме так буде повалено всі народи світу.</p>"},"note28a":{"id":"note28a","marker":"28а","pid":"121077159","context":"року","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077198\" id=\"note28a_p1\"><small>ТОБТО</small> прибл. у 720 р. до <span class=\"small-caps\">р.х.</span> цей тягар або послання про засудження було пророковано про филистимлян, у той час як Юдея буде в безпеці.</p>"},"note28b":{"id":"note28b","marker":"28б","pid":"121077159","context":"Ахаз","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077199\" id=\"note28b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/16.20?lang=ukr#p20\">2 Цар. 16:20</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/16.20?lang=ukr#p20","text":"2 Цар. 16:20"}]},"note32a":{"id":"note32a","marker":"32а","pid":"121077163","context":"Сіон","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077200\" id=\"note32a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/zion?lang=ukr\"><small>ПП</small> Сіон</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/zion?lang=ukr","text":"ПП Сіон"}]},"note32b":{"id":"note32b","marker":"32б","pid":"121077163","context":"бідні","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077201\" id=\"note32b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.12?lang=ukr#p12\">Соф. 3:12</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/ot/zeph/3.12?lang=ukr#p12","text":"Соф. 3:12"}]},"note32c":{"id":"note32c","marker":"32в","pid":"121077163","context":"покладатимуться","text":"<p data-aid=\"121077202\" id=\"note32c_p1\"><small>АБО</small> шукати притулку.</p>"}}},"pids